posts.post_title: FS A42 Kimball Album pages inc Dempsey and A. Oakley.
posts.post_content:
FS Groupnof 9 non Sport Kimball Album Pages. Including Jack Dempsey page and Annie Oakley page. Represents 36 of the 50 cards in the set. To complete album would need I think 3 pages and the cover.  Asking $300 net to me  for the 9 pages. Not looking to split up this group. They are a beautiful display and PSA will encase and grade as Authentic individual pages. 
Thanks for looking 


Jonathan
